name: #1 El comienzo
description:
The child was left behind. A new reality is seen. Privacy is an obsolete concept that was lost during 
the digitalization of reality, at the dawn of the Information Society, 
in the pursuit of the privilege of being informed every second. 
You are the one who has exposed your privacy to the world and,
 believe it or not, you do not want it back. 
How will it all end? the story goes on.
